        Every dollar helps us amplify voices and create opportunities for those who make plays that matter
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Impact Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4 text-center">üéôÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 text-center">Storytelling Platform</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Providing athletes and creators with the tools and audience to share their stories and make an impact
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Impact Card 2 -->
