      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Exclusive apparel and merchandise that represents more than just a brand‚Äîit's a statement.
        Show the world that you stand for courage, action, and legacy.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-10">
